    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://projects.propublica.org/toddler-formula-documents">
                                    Documents Show Internal Clash Before U.S. Officials Pushed to Weaken Toddler Formula Rules
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Government documents obtained by ProPublica show a stark rift between trade and health officials over international efforts to regulate toddler milk. The records provide a rare, candid glimpse into U.S. policymaking around children&#039;s health.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/lucas-waldron">Lucas Waldron</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/heather-vogell">Heather Vogell</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-03-21EDT05:05">March 21, 5:05 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    


                    
    
