    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/the-rising-cost-of-the-oil-industrys-slow-death">
                                    The Rising Cost of the Oil Industry’s Slow Death
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Unplugged oil and gas wells accelerate climate change, threaten public health and risk hitting taxpayers’ pocketbooks. ProPublica and Capital &amp; Main found that the money set aside to fix the problem falls woefully short of the impending cost.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/mark-olalde">Mark Olalde</a>, ProPublica, and <span class="name">Nick Bowlin</span>, <a href="https://capitalandmain.com/">Capital &amp; Main</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-02-22EST05:00">Feb. 22, 5 a.m. EST</time>
